---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Fast Easy - Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Fast Easy - Fasting Timer iOS app."
  ogUrl="https://idlefusion.com/fast-easy/privacy"
>
  <main>
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-12">Fast Easy - Fasting Timer &middot; Effective February 11, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
            <p>Fast Easy does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. Everything stays on your device.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
            <p>All fasting sessions, history, and preferences are stored locally on your device using SwiftData. No data is sent to any server, cloud service, or third party. There are no user accounts and no sign-up required.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Analytics & Tracking</h2>
            <p>Fast Easy contains no analytics frameworks, no ad SDKs, no tracking pixels, and no telemetry of any kind. We do not use any third-party services that collect data.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Network Usage</h2>
            <p>Fast Easy makes no network requests. The app works entirely offline. The only network activity associated with the app is through the App Store for updates.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>Fast Easy does not knowingly collect any information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>If this policy changes, we will update this page with the new effective date. Since Fast Easy collects no data, meaningful changes are unlikely.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
